reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars They suck now
reviews.reviewText: I have used this brand of screen protector for my last three iPhones (12 mini, 14 pro, and now 15 pro). They used to fit perfectly and were great. But not anymore. The version for the 15 pro is too big. IT ALSO NO LONGER COMES WITH AN ALIGNMENT FRAME. That’s a big deal for me as the frame makes these exponential easier to install. While this brand used to be an amazing product for the price, now you just get what you pay for.
